text:
Good job, Kogane.
Are you ready to head back?

Well, not quite yet...
I still have a lot of luggage to pack...

Haha, take your time, it's okay.
How was the training camp?

It was so much fun!
I'm feeling sad that it's ending today.

You still seem full of energy.
Even though you were busy making everyone's dinner.

When someone enjoys my cookin',
it makes me feel energetic too!

I had fun makin' champon for everyone~
They said it was delicious...

Fuyuko said she'd only have a little bit,
but she ended up eatin' a full plate.

Next time we have a trainin' camp, shall we make plate udon?
Hehe, my dreams are expandin'~
